      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, just pure driving bliss. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and it\u2019s been serviced religiously. You won't find another one in this kind of pristine shape. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
