    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric performance. This unit features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS variable valve timing system for an uncompromising 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring visceral feedback and optimal power delivery. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Every bushing, link, and damper remains in peak operational condition, preserving the original suspension geometry. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. This is a turn-key, analog masterpiece for the discerning driver who demands mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
