    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and the exterior reflects that care with a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic feature\u2014from the advanced navigation system to the ambient lighting\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It includes a comprehensive binder of all service records, showing strictly scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is clean, and the car handles with the tightness and precision of a brand-new machine. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence. Seeing is believing\u2014this is undoubtedly the cleanest specimen currently available on the market.",
